# Google Maps API proxy → serverless function (true server-side proxy, no CORS)
/api/maps/*    /.netlify/functions/google-places/:splat    200!
/api/places/*  /.netlify/functions/google-places/place/:splat  200!

# Profile QR routes → serverless function (instant HTML page + OG tags)
/u/*    /.netlify/functions/profile   200

# SPA catch-all — must come AFTER the specific rules above
/*      /index.html                   200
